page.name: Rubik's Club
page.description: Rubik's club is a club for anyone interested in connecting and cubing.  We have a very friendly and welcoming group of students who spend time connecting, talking, and sharing strategies for solving a variety of cubes.  We keep track of every participant's different solves and times to see improvement week to week.  If you enjoy meeting new people who also love cubing, this is the place for you.
